        </g>
        <g transform="translate(350 514)">
          <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="18" />
          <path d="M-9 0 H9" />
          <path d="M0 -9 V9" />
          <text x="30" y="6">Retries</text>
        </g>
        <g transform="translate(564 514)">
          <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="18" />
          <path d="M-7 8 L0 -8 L7 8" />
          <text x="30" y="6">Deploy / Migrate</text>
        </g>
        <g transform="translate(864 514)">
          <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="18" />
          <circle cx="0" cy="0" r="5" />
          <text x="30" y="6">Observability</text>
        </g>
      </g>

      <g class="langgraph-state-capsule" filter="url(#lg-glow)">
        <rect x="0" y="0" width="86" height="34" rx="17" />
        <circle cx="18" cy="17" r="8" />
        <text x="34" y="22">STATE</text>
      </g>
    </svg>

    <div class="langgraph-callouts">
      <article class="langgraph-callout langgraph-callout--state">
        <span class="langgraph-callout__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="4" y="6" width="16" height="12" rx="4" /><circle cx="9" cy="12" r="2.2" /></svg>
        </span>
        <div>
          <h3>State is the payload</h3>
          <p>The capsule moving through the yard is shared state, not the prompt text itself.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="langgraph-callout langgraph-callout--routing">
        <span class="langgraph-callout__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 6v12" /><path d="M5 12h8" /><path d="M13 12l6-5" /><path d="M13 12l6 5" /></svg>
        </span>
        <div>
          <h3>Routing is explicit</h3>
          <p>Switches, edges, and review branches are architecture, not hidden loop logic.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="langgraph-callout langgraph-callout--interrupt">
        <span class="langgraph-callout__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 4v8" /><circle cx="12" cy="16.5" r="3.5" /><path d="M5 8h14" /></svg>
        </span>
        <div>
          <h3>Humans can interrupt</h3>
          <p>Approval and edits happen through a visible gate with a clean resume path.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="langgraph-callout langgraph-callout--durability">
        <span class="langgraph-callout__icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><ellipse cx="12" cy="7" rx="6.5" ry="3" /><path d="M5.5 7v9c0 1.7 2.9 3 6.5 3s6.5-1.3 6.5-3V7" /></svg>
        </span>
        <div>
          <h3>Durability makes it real</h3>
          <p>Checkpointing, memory, and thread history are the floor that makes recovery possible.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
